    PUBG Global Championship

    IntroducingPUBG Global Esports

    Competitive seasons are aligned on the calendar to create a full slate of professional leagues and unique tournaments around the world. After a season of weekly league battles and high profile special events, top teams from every region come together in the fall for the most prestigious live event in battle royale esports: the PUBG Global Championship.
